title: Not All Victory Laps Are Victorious
description:
Domonique and Charlie recap MNF and the Rams terrible offense. Then, they debate if we're numb to Patrick Mahomes' greatness before getting into the transition point in the NFL where we're ushering out older QB's to make way for the young stars. Lastly, Ashley Foxworth returns for another segment of Roses & Thorns.
